description: Try our easy to follow Gluten-Free Banana Bread Muffins recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Gluten-Free Banana Bread Muffins Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 0.5 cup gluten-free Macro natural almond kernels
400 g Free From Gluten banana bread mix

recipeInstructions.text: Bake muffins for 20 minutes or until golden and a skewer inserted in centres comes out clean. Cool in pan for 10 minutes. Transfer to a wire rack to cool completely before serving.
